# Riskr — environment variables
#
# The leaderboard API (api/leaderboard.js) stores scores in Upstash Redis.
# Copy this file to ".env.local" for local dev, or set these in the Vercel
# dashboard (Project → Settings → Environment Variables) for production.
#
# Two naming schemes are supported. You only need ONE set:
#
# 1) Vercel Marketplace "Upstash" integration injects these automatically:
KV_REST_API_URL=
KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
#
# 2) A direct Upstash account gives you these instead:
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
